e": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031574_7368380123202802_7558905963144694006_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TWcy3nilYiIQ7kNvgHHQrt3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCuqaVk_O_TRCuJCnEf04l3HDGaaHSi6O7P_MRrnL4aHQ&oe=66DD982F"}, {"file_name": "Icon512x512.png", "id": "1670336176664074", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982460_1670336179997407_7260350772183686599_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4hOatF2FAG0Q7kNvgGh6NO4&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB00bnB-Rv2y1xndrh2ouFIRKfahN1uaNKqK60kIEOJHw&oe=66DDA547"}]}, "id": "718554092403278", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Final4.png", "id": "1064564687657120", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031458_1064564694323786_2934528766626345290_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WTArLrQPw_wQ7kNvgFpF1t2&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDynt_kcAPt2HBY8WguazC9KMOHE8EujeBk6iLABB1ZAA&oe=66DD7F9E"}, {"file_name": "Final1.png", "id": "934483367267393", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984460_934483370600726_2342269543366152476_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vvtLTx-AAl8Q7kNvgFmeEME&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBFaMkmqRpezBnJ301CB-K7G8EPKCVd0njd3C8ujSU0Pw&oe=66DD7373"}, {"file_name": "Final5.png", "id": "1109469673205956", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031326_1109469676539289_4268533616333460252_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MdAAZWYDHkYQ7kNvgEyOSVb&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDDSEka-y4Jpo_5G66Qnoj-qA4NBD9Of4quDw_tN1yoUQ&oe=66DD71F7"}, {"file_name": "Final2.png", "id": "916532898880837", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003274_916532902214170_6367672695544734699_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PC_RLuHnhgIQ7kNvgF5kq_e&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDGbg_XTxpEt6mWoy7yrD8nvlU5VIEaYP8IS9k5NjpnAg&oe=66DD9A3A"}, {"file_name": "Final3.png", "id": "1165340330878993", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974677_1165340334212326_9147485654240656059_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=P5PGzjySLRgQ7kNvgGSNnE5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAewv7GjB9yRNtRfw0PVTmSPOSztsInyElJdf1iToa6Lg&oe=66DD7507"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Light Up The Dark", "keywords": [], "long_description": "*  Finger Controls.  \"Play\" the fireworks with your right-hand fingers using individual fingers and \"chords\" of fingers to fire different types of fire works.\n*  The Color Ball.  Your left hand is the color ball, moving side-to-side changes the color of the firework, and up/down adjusts the size of the fireworks blasts.\n*  Seamlessly switch between hands and controllers (with a hardware delay).\n*  Play reclined or laying down!  Or upside down.  Any position, any space.\n*  Environmental features such as snow, falling leaves, fireflies, and bubbles.  Seriously, try the bubbles.\n*  Listen to various audio tracks including a gentle Mozart piece, a Sousa March, and Wagner's Ride of the Valkyries, adjustable volumes for music and fireworks.\n*  Set the weather and the Speed of Time.  Note, the weather has a mind of its own.  \n*  Show and hide individual UI components or enter the VOID, with no user interface other than the finger streaks.\n\nShow and hide individual UI components or enter the ", "short_description": "Light Up The Dark is an exciting firework experience featuring a highly customizable atmosphere and snowman modes for casual or gaming fun.  Advanced controls using fingers and hands provide a unique experience.\n\nEnjoy a zen world with a light snow and the sounds of the forest at night, with fireworks.  \n\n\u200bOr bend time so a day lasts a few seconds, with a Sousa march fillings your ears while snowmen crash any sense of tranquility, with fireworks.\n\nYour fireworks.  Your way."}]}